snippet.title: Another Adventure in NSMBU - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Another Adventure in NSMBU:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dAj5bjp9JdQ0gcyYqtsneTryNcg7INkM/view?usp=sharing

Another Adventure in NSMBU OST Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3gfc1EGc7k&list=PLht8fDHc_0XSh9_GQHWEaFMGS9-9DJaYd

My YouTube Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcMzDyuMfLSlVFaIKh72Tdg

If you have any questions or problems with the hack, contact me on discord:
Ravid # 2991

Another Adventure in NSMBU is my first NSMBU hack that I release and I'm really happy that it is out now! But keep in mind that this is my first NSMBU hack, so don't expect too much! But I hope, you enjoy the hack!

The hack contains:
- 4 completely new worlds with 36 new levels
- a retextured worldmap
- custom music
- custom tilesets
- some custom backgrounds
and much more!

Full Credits:

- Level Design: Davetendo
- Custom Tilesets: Rimea, Davetendo
- Logo: DayownerTV
- Custom World Map: Davetendo
- Custom Music: Davetendo (Soundtrack: Nintendo, Newer Team)
- Custom Backgrounds: WillyMaker, Davetendo
- Custom Sprites: Deserted U Team, Davetendo
- Level Names: Davetendo
- Visual Inspiration: Nintendo, Newer Team, Rimea, WillyMaker
- Tools: AboodXD, KillzXGaming
- Testing: Davetendo, DayownerTV, Nyrotrax
- General Support: DayownerTV, Nyrotrax
- ORIGINAL GAME: NINTENDO

#AnotherAdventureinNSMBU, #NewSuperMarioBrosU, #NSMBU, #SuperMario
